%div#certifications-generate(ng-controller="CertificationsGenerateController" ng-init="generate.init()")
  %div{'ng-include' => asset_path('certifications/_header.html').inspect}

  .row(style="padding-top: 20px")
    .col.col-md-12
      :markdown
        Download the VA Form 8 and **verify** all the fields are **accurate**.  When finished, the appeal will be **certified** to the Board of Appeals.

      %hr

  %a(ng-href="/files/forms/{{certifications.data.info.file_name}}") Download Complete Form 8

  %hr

  .input-group
    %a.my-form-button(data-label="Go Back" data-icon="chevron-left" ng-href="#/certifications/{{certifications.data.info.bfkey}}/questions")
    &nbsp;
    %a.my-form-button(data-label="Finish Certification" data-icon="chevron-right" data-color="primary" ng-href="#/certifications/{{certifications.data.info.bfkey}}/finish")
